      "title": "DMC issues Landslide alert for several areas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Disaster Management Center (DMC) had issued a landslide alert for several areas, active for the next 24 hours.",
        "Accordingly, the landslide alert has been issued for Baddegama and Yakkalamulla Divisional Secretariats of Galle, Bulathsinhala and Palindanuwara Divisional Secretariats of Kalutara and fr Ratnapura, Elapatha and Kuruwita Divisional Secretariats of Ratnapura.",
        "The Department also issued a Red alert for heavy rains, citing a \u00a0low-level atmospheric disturbance in the vicinity of Sri Lanka.",
        "Accordingly, very heavy showers above 150mm may occur at some places in Western, Southern, Sabaragamuwa, Central and Uva provinces on Wednesday (31), while heavy showers about",
